<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your Login Code</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
        .header {
            padding: 40px 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1a1a1a;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px;
        }
        .content p {
            margin: 0 0 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #4a4a4a;
        }
        .code-container {
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 24px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .code-label {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #757575;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        .code {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            letter-spacing: 8px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .info-box {
            background-color: #f0f7ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #2196F3;
            padding: 16px;
            margin: 24px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .info-box p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #1565C0;
        }
        .footer {
            padding: 30px 40px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin: 0 0 10px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #9e9e9e;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #2196F3;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .header, .content, .footer {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            .code {
                font-size: 28px;
                letter-spacing: 4px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Login Verification</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello,</p>
            <p>You requested a login code to access your account. Use the code below to complete your sign-in:</p>

            <div class="code-container">
                <div class="code-label">Your Login Code</div>
                <div class="code">{{SINGLE_PASS}}</div>
            </div>

            <p>If you didn't request this code, you can safely ignore this email. Your account remains secure.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</p>
            <p>If you need assistance, please contact our support team.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
